thread.title: Elena Strugariu

author: Elena Strugariu
title: Elena Strugariu
text: Sam made my new online store from scratch with a great and original design, the best apps that helped me to grow my conversions. If you are commited and you want results than I highly recommend Enxlevel Academy. Sam is a fantastic guy, he gave his support everytime that I needed and I know that he will do the same in the future. I stay with a good friend and a good experience. Thank you and definitely we will have more projects together.
